The Ultimate TRS-80 Cassette Data Cable (All Tandy Models That USE 5-PIN DIN) PLANS-SCHEMATICS

These Plans and Schematics are for the ULTIMATE UBER TRS-80 Data Cassette Cable for all TRS-80 Tandy Models that use the 5-Pin DIN cassette interface cable. You just have to see this. Only the two .pdf&#039;s are actually required - the other stuff is just misc. trs-80 stuff and some DVD sources. You can download only the pdf&#039;s or the whole thing, by selecting the files in your bittorrent application.

Works with the TRS-80 MODEL 100, 101, 200, 1, 3, 4, ETC AND ALL COLOUR COMPUTER (COCO) MODELS INCLUDING THE MC-10.

Can conceivable be adapted to anything such as the Sinclair ZX81 or Timex Sinclair 1000, ZX-Spectrum, TS-2068, etc.

Enjoy :-)
